      "x_post_id": "2075731830477877612",
      "notes": "Extreme low-resource inference engine for GLM-5.2 744B MoE (~40B active params). Pure C, zero dependencies, streams experts from disk while keeping dense part (~17B params, ~9.9GB int4) resident in RAM. Enables flagship-scale local inference on ~25GB laptop / no GPU. CLI chat + OpenAI-compatible serve mode. Tradeoff: low tokens/s (0.05-1+ tok/s on consumer NVMe). High novelty, rapid adoption signal (2k+ stars quickly). Strong fit for local agent pipelines needing massive reasoning/context on constrained hardware. Integrates via serve endpoint + LiteLLM. See sources/x-posts.md for X seed analysis and community speed notes. Pinned recent main (Tauri desktop addition)."
    },
